data.title: The NAMES Project AIDS Memorial Quilt: List of Names 1992-1993
data.meta_description: This booklet contains the complete [alphabetical] list of names included in the NAMES Project AIDS Memorial Quilt as of July 15, 1992. The four-digit number next to each name indicates the 12'x12' block in which the panel is grouped.
